name: searching_by_keyword_pen_should_display_the_corresponding_article

testSteps.description: Should see definition: A tool, originally made from a feather but now usually a small tubular instrument, containing ink used to write or make marks.

exception.message:
Expected: a collection containing a string containing "A tool, originally made from a feather but now usually a small tubular instrument, containing ink used to write or make marks."
     but: was "An enclosure (enclosed area) used to contain domesticated animals, especially sheep or cattle.
There are two steers in the third pen.", was "(slang) A prison cell.
They caught him with a stolen horse, and he wound up in the pen again.", was "(baseball) The bullpen.
Two righties are up in the pen."
